<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="already-adv">already <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɔːl'redi/    美 /ɔːl'redi/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>已经：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>[表示在某个时间之前]：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We have already had a discussion over the plan. 
我们已对这项计划进行了讨论。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>[常用于句尾] [表示惊奇或意外]：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Is it 5 o’clock already? 
已经5点了吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You can’t be hungry already — you had lunch only two hours ago! 
你不会又饿了吧——你可是两小时前刚吃完午饭！</p><footer>2008 浙江</footer></div>

<p>注: already一般用在肯定句中，在否定句和疑问句中多用yet。  </p></div>